Key Match Events: Chourio's HR puts Brewers ahead in the 9th, beat Reds
Miscellaneous Highlights: The Brewers needed to win by 2 runs or more to cover the spread.
The over/under was 8.5 and the teams scored 9 runs, so people who bet the over won
The Brewers won at -131 odds so a bet of $131 won $231 total
